    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと！　テントが燃えてるじゃない！\n二人とも、早く消すわよ！",
      "startTime": 4.7333334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-01-night",
      "startTime": 7.1666667938
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……隣のカップルのせいね\nキャンプファイヤー、派手に燃やしてたみたいだから",
      "startTime": 10.9333334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "恋も炎も燃え上がったって？\n他人のテントまで燃やしてんじゃないわよ！",
      "startTime": 16.6000021617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-01-night",
      "startTime": 19.133335495
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてこんなことになっちゃったのかしら……",
      "startTime": 19.133335495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-01-night",
      "startTime": 19.9387299855
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数週間前",
      "startTime": 24.200000151,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1285.8263414,
          "startTime": 25.4858264924
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 25.1666669448
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふーん、ふん\n佐伯遙子のミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！",
      "startTime": 28.3333353917,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "やけにご機嫌じゃない。どうしたの？",
      "startTime": 32.0000020583,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "とうとう、あの名物企画『ミラクル☆アイドル\nバースデー！』のお話をいただいたの！",
      "startTime": 38.2333343744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルのやりたいことを\nなんでも叶えてくれるなんて、わくわくしない？",
      "startTime": 42.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "お仕事だけど、結構自由にやらせてもらえるものね\n何するか決まったの？",
      "startTime": 49.6666697423,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "実は、この日のためにずっと考えてたことがあって\n莉央さん、私と一緒にキャンプに行かない？",
      "startTime": 56.4000028212,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}